extends ./layouts/marketing-cloud.pug

//- TIPS:
//- 1. Artworks's path should be relative to "src" folder;
//- 2. Alternative SVG Artworks are available here:
       https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@contactlab/ds-tokens/artworks/
//- 3. Use <p> html tag for split sentences;
//- 4. Use <article> html tag for split paragraphs;
//----------------------------------------------------------------

block content

  //--- Artworks
  - const IMG_SRC = `${CLAB_DS_TOKENS}/artworks/warn-api.svg`

  //--- Titles
  - const EN_TITLE= "The application has encountered an unknown error"
  - const IT_TITLE= "L'applicazione ha riscontrato un errore sconosciuto"

  //--- EN Content
  mixin EN_BODY()
    article
      p It doesn't appear to have affected your data, but our technical staff have been automatically notified and will be looking into this with the utmost urgency.

    article
      p Help us improve your experience by #[a(href="https://contactlab.com/en/contact-us" title="Customer Care") sending an error report].

  //--- IT Content
  mixin IT_BODY()
    article
      p Non sembra aver influito sui tuoi dati, ma il nostro personale tecnico è stato informato automaticamente e lo esaminerà con la massima urgenza.

    article
      p Aiutaci a migliorare la tua esperienza #[a(href="https://contactlab.com/it/contact-us" title="Servizio Clienti") inviando una segnalazione di errore].
